(SUBJECT:) Tj T*
(Application requesting suspension and dismissal of trustees of Shri Vajreshwari) Tj T*
(Yogini Devi Sansthan for violations of the Trust Deed, Maharashtra Public Trusts) Tj T*
(Act 1950 and Income Tax laws; and for immediate appointment of an Administrator.) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(--- BACKGROUND ---) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(1. I, Shri Narayan Kondu Thakare, am a former employee of Shri Vajreshwari) Tj T*
(   Yogini Devi Sansthan. Having worked 13 years as Accountant/Cashier and) Tj T*
(   20 years as Secretary, and an additional 2 years post-retirement as) Tj T*
(   In-charge Secretary, I am fully acquainted with the affairs of the temple) Tj T*
(   and have its best interests at heart.) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(2. Shri Vajreshwari Yogini Devi Sansthan is a public charitable trust) Tj T*
(   registered on 27/05/1952 under the Maharashtra Public Trusts Act 1950,) Tj T*
(   with Registration No. A\(192\) Thane.) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(3. In Trustee Appointment Inquiry No. 12/2019, the Hon. District Court,) Tj T*
(   Thane, by order dated 31/08/2019, appointed the following 5 trustees) Tj T*
(   for a period of 5 years:) Tj T*
(   1\) Shri Madhukar Ramchandra Patkar        - Chairman) Tj T*
(   2\) Shri Dhanesh Hemendra Gosavi           - Hereditary Trustee) Tj T*
(   3\) Shri Milind Yashwant Chorghe           - Trustee) Tj T*
(   4\) Dr. Vivek Ramchandra Patil             - Trustee) Tj T*
(   5\) Shri Raju Shantaram Patil              - Trustee) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(4. The Board of Trustees took charge of the Sansthan on 13/09/2019.) Tj T*
ET
